metadata.name: Divine Intervention
metadata.description:
"Angelus Pacis" is a breathtaking and emotionally charged collection of images that portray everyday people as angelic figures, courageously helping those in the midst of war. Through the images, we are reminded that even in the darkest of times, there are still angels among us, working tirelessly to bring peace and healing to a troubled world.

1/1 Editions by Antti Karppinen
